Package: earthR
Type: Package
Title: Earthquake Visualization Tools Package for the NOAA Significant Earthquake Database
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gustavo Bruges
Maintainer:Gustavo Bruges <rcientificos@gmail.com>
Description: This is an Earthquake Visualization Tools Package for the NOAA Significant Earthquake Database.  The package includes tools to map the earthquakes along a timeline and to display the earthquakes geographically on a map.
   The earthquaketools package was written for the Mastering Software Development in R Capstone Class in June 2018.
